"Commercial Use" includes any paid, revenue-generating, client, enterprise, or production activity, whether direct or indirect.

"Production Use" means deploying, running, or integrating the Software in any environment accessed by users other than the developer, whether internal or external.

"Internal Evaluation" means testing or experimentation within an organization, without delivering the Software to clients, customers, or production users.

